<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idcc694900-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70" identifier="/us/usc/t49/s47531"><num value="47531">§ 47531.</num><heading> Penalties</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">A person violating section 47528, 47529, 47530, or 47534 of this title or a regulation prescribed under any of those sections is subject to the same civil penalties and procedures under chapter 463 of this title as a person violating section 44701(a) or (b) or any of sections 44702–44716 of this title.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idcc694901-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70">(<ref href="/us/pl/103/272/s1/e">Pub. L. 103–272, § 1(e)</ref>, <date date="1994-07-05">July 5, 1994</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/108/1293">108 Stat. 1293</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/103/429/s6/73">Pub. L. 103–429, § 6(73)</ref>, <date date="1994-10-31">Oct. 31, 1994</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/108/4388">108 Stat. 4388</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/112/95/tV/s506/b/1">Pub. L. 112–95, title V, § 506(b)(1)</ref>, <date date="2012-02-14">Feb. 14, 2012</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/126/106">126 Stat. 106</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
